This is the Darkqueer Theme by [[*user Queerious]], a fork of the existing [[[*theme:blankstyle|BLANKSTYLE]]], by [[*user Placeholder McD]] and [[*user HarryBlank]], and intended to be a darker alternative to [[[theme:Queerstyle]]].

This theme also uses the [[[*component:pride-highlighter|White Outline Classic LGBTQ+ Pride Logo]]] by [[*user Woedenaz]].

This theme completely recolors the page, and modifies standard components to be a neutral/dark tone. It also changes styling to a pseudo-futurism vibe.

